    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.44
    v0 = v0
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.exp((v0 + 0.63 - v0 + 0.28)))
    v1 = (tmp * wp.cos(0.85))
    v1 = 0.74
    v2 = wp.exp(tmp)
    v2 = (v2 + (wp.exp(v1 + 0.82) - (v1 + 0.08 + v2 + 0.57)))
